      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This meticulously maintained specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in untouched, original state. Every service milestone has been documented, ensuring that its mechanical integrity matches its exceptional aesthetic appeal. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this vehicle offers an uncompromising driving experience and long-term value.",
