      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Wrapped in a coat of Deep Midnight Pearl that catches the moon\u2019s reflection like a still lake, this machine is more than a car\u2014it\u2019s a time capsule of pure elegance. Slide into the cockpit, where the scent of hand-stitched saddle leather greets you like an old friend, and the engine hums with the steady, rhythmic heartbeat of a champion. Every curve of its silhouette whispers stories of sun-drenched coastal drives and moonlit escapes. This is a rare opportunity to own a masterpiece that feels as though it just rolled off the artisan\u2019s floor\u2014a pristine companion ready to write your next great chapter with every turn of the key.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
